name: The Trans-Interdimensional Laboursaving Transportation service
description:
Fancy a trip around the multiverse?
See the sights!
Travel to mind bending dimensions!
Get awestruck!
Get confused!

All these experiences can be yours dear customer for one measly download, what's holding you back?

Made as an entry for Ludum Dare 37 with the theme "One Room". All art assets were created in the VR paint program Tilt Brush.
developers: Alexander Birke aka Out Of Bounds Games
